  <dialog id="about">
    <br>
    <div style="font-size: 24px; position:absolute; left:50px; color: #ffac13;">POV-Lab</div>
    <br><br>
    This is an online tool for creating <a href="https://povray.org" target="_blank">POV-Ray</a> scenes in a web browser and rendering them on a server by <a href="https://wiki.povray.org/content/User:Le_Forgeron" target="_blank">HgPovray</a>. Send scene to rendering by clicking [Upload] button on top panel or pressing [Ctrl-S], use [Camera] button to view rendered image in AR.</p>
    <p>Following tutorials are available online:
    <a href="https://povlab.online/povtutorial/" target="_blank">Basics</a>,
    <a href="https://povlab.online/animtutorial/" target="_blank">Animation</a>,
    <a href="https://povlab.online/isotutorial/" target="_blank">Isosurfaces</a>.
    Use them to explore endless features of one of the best ray tracers in the world !</p>
